Kat M commented on a card: <https://trello.com/card/532930786e6d6abf08624285/53293416d888f7ad22c4995b|Lock>
Lock now takes commands and does not update the UI until the command has been set. There are still edge cases to consider, like what happens when a command has been sent, and then the mood is changed?

Kat M commented on a card: <https://trello.com/card/532930786e6d6abf08624285/532937c6648307664f49ec94|Sign off (or replace) icons in build>
icons are all up to date
<@U0260V1BX>: should I treat the outlets like the lock? in that “disable” in the mood means that it doesn’t change? or should I treat it like the lights where “disable” turns them off?

[dexter/] 2 new commits:
[dexter/] <https://bitbucket.org/uncorkedstudios/dexter/commits/f0a4ec428ae1cfbec2cab90f1fa102c527719126|f0a4ec428ae1>: updated quickmenu icons from roomba to navibot
